Modifications by GodricTM, for Meta Portal devices and the Immortal launcher:
  - Repackaged as applicationId "com.portal.tts" with Portal-specific branding
    (name, icon, FileProvider authority).
  - Voice/model auto-detection (VoiceCatalog) for Kokoro multilingual and Piper
    Romanian voices loaded from external storage.
  - Build/manifest adjustments for sideloading on Portal hardware (ARM64).

